# Band 8 Sample Answer

## Introduction

The two line graphs illustrate changes in the proportion of households owning three electrical appliances — washing machines, refrigerators and vacuum cleaners — as well as the average amount of time spent on housework per week in one country between 1920 and 2019.

**翻译：**
这两张折线图展示了1920年至2019年间某国拥有三种家用电器（洗衣机、冰箱和吸尘器）的家庭比例变化，以及每户每周用于家务劳动的平均时间变化。

---

## Overview

Overall, ownership of all three electrical appliances increased significantly over the period, with refrigerators and vacuum cleaners becoming almost universal by the end of the timeline. At the same time, the number of hours spent on housework declined dramatically, indicating that technological development greatly reduced domestic workload.

**翻译：**
总体来看，这三种家电的家庭拥有率在该时期均显著上升，其中冰箱和吸尘器在时间末期几乎实现普及。同时，每周家务劳动时间大幅下降，这表明科技发展极大减轻了家庭劳动负担。

---

## Body Paragraph 1

In 1920, washing machines were the most commonly owned appliance, with approximately 40% of households possessing one, compared with 30% for vacuum cleaners and almost 0% for refrigerators. Over the following decades, ownership of all appliances rose steadily. Refrigerator ownership experienced the most dramatic growth, climbing to around 90% in 1960 before reaching full penetration in 1980, after which it remained stable. Likewise, the proportion of households with vacuum cleaners increased continuously, reaching 100% by 2000. Although washing machine ownership also rose overall, it experienced a slight decline from 70% in 1960 to about 65% in 1980 before recovering to roughly 75% in 2019.

**翻译：**
1920年，洗衣机是最普及的家电，大约40%的家庭拥有洗衣机，而吸尘器的比例为30%，冰箱几乎为零。在接下来的几十年中，所有家电的拥有率都稳步上升。其中冰箱增长最为显著，到1960年已达到约90%，并于1980年达到100%，此后保持稳定。同样，吸尘器的拥有率也持续增长，并于2000年达到100%。尽管洗衣机的拥有率总体呈上升趋势，但其在1960年至1980年间从70%略微下降至约65%，随后回升至2019年的约75%。

---

## Body Paragraph 2

Corresponding to the rise in appliance ownership, the amount of time spent on housework fell considerably throughout the century. In 1920, households spent around 50 hours per week on domestic tasks such as cleaning, cooking and washing clothes. This figure then decreased steadily to 35 hours in 1940 and 20 hours in 1960. After falling further to approximately 15 hours in 1980, the number remained unchanged in 2000 before dropping slightly to around 10 hours per week in 2019.

**翻译：**
与家电拥有率上升相对应的是，家庭用于家务劳动的时间在整个世纪中显著下降。1920年，家庭每周大约花费50小时进行清洁、做饭和洗衣等家务劳动。该数字随后稳步下降，1940年降至35小时，1960年降至20小时。1980年进一步降至约15小时后，2000年保持不变，最终在2019年略微下降至每周约10小时。

---

# ⭐ 这篇 8 分 Task 1 的关键写法

## ✅ 1. Overview 一定写“趋势”

高分 overview 不只是：

❌ ownership increased

而是：

✅ appliances became almost universal
✅ housework declined dramatically

这叫：

# “概括趋势 + 总结结果”

---

# ⭐ 这篇里的高级表达（直接积累）

## 描述“大幅增长”

> experienced the most dramatic growth

> climbed to around 90%

> reached full penetration

“full penetration” 很高级，表示：

# “完全普及”

---

## 描述“轻微下降”

> experienced a slight decline

雅思特别喜欢：

* slight decline
* marginal decrease
* modest rise

这种“程度副词”。

---

## 描述“对应关系”

> Corresponding to the rise in appliance ownership...

这个句型特别适合：

* 图表联动
* 因果趋势
* 双图比较

属于 Band 8 常见写法。

---

# ⭐ 这篇为什么像 Band 8？

因为它：

✅ 有清晰 overview
✅ 不机械报数字
✅ 有趋势总结
✅ 会比较不同数据
✅ 使用高级动词（climb / recover / decline）
✅ 有复杂句和从句
✅ 数据选择合理，不堆数字

真正的高分 Task 1：

# 不是“念数据”

而是：

# 👉 “描述变化 + 概括趋势 + 进行比较”
